        <prj:note>The main goal of this proposal is to determine the 12C/13C, 16O/18O  and 14N/15N  isotopic ratios in CO and HCN, 
in order to constrain the formation and origin of these species in Neptunes atmosphere. 
This frequency setup -1- allows to measure the C18O(3-2), 13CO(3-2) and HC15N(4-3) transitions in band 7.
Combined with the other frequency setup -2- it will allow to derive the searched isotopic ratios.
These unique measurements will add new constraints on the atmosphere history and the origin of CO and HCN.
